# NSProgressIndicator.Style.spinning

**Case**

A small circular indicator that can be determinate or indeterminate.

## Declaration

```swift
case spinning
```

## Discussion

The appearance of a determinate spinning style indicator is similar to an animated pie chart.

## Constants

- **NSProgressIndicator.Style.bar**: A rectangular indicator that can be determinate or indeterminate.
